2025-09-07 19:02:33 - StudioAtrium\Entity\User\Message:Update {"timestamp":1757271753,"user_id":16934,"user_ip":"178.43.220.31","user_browser":"Mozilla\/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit\/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome\/139.0.0.0 Safari\/537.36 Edg\/139.0.0.0","dao_classname":"StudioAtrium\\Entity\\User\\Message\\DAO\\PDOMySQL","dao_event":"dao_object_update","entity_classname":"StudioAtrium\\Entity\\User\\Message","entity_data":{"id":1423,"__foreign_props":[],"user_id":"16934","parent_id":"1422","author":"Studio Atrium","title":"Re: Projekt","message":"<p>Dzie\u0144 dobry<\/p>\r\n<p>Pani Lidio, wysy\u0142ali\u015bmy materia\u0142y, czasami na poczcie wp wpadaj\u0105 one do r\u00f3\u017cnych folder\u00f3w (oferty, spam), prosz\u0119 przegl\u0105dn\u0105\u0107 sobie zawarto\u015b\u0107 poczty w tych miejscach, tam powinny by\u0107 materia\u0142y do projektu.<br \/>Je\u017celi nadal ich Pani nie znajdzie, prosz\u0119 o informacj\u0119.<\/p>\r\n<p>Pozdrawiam<br \/>\u0141ukasz Jakubiec<\/p>","create_date":"2025-09-02 09:37:50","status":"read","attachments":[],"_uid":364324},"entity_changes":{"status":"read"}}
