2025-09-09 10:52:23 - StudioAtrium\Entity\Discuss\Post:Insert {"timestamp":1757415143,"user_id":null,"user_ip":"156.228.95.108","user_browser":"Mozilla\/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit\/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome\/114.0.0.0 Safari\/537.36 Edg\/114.0.1264.71","dao_classname":"StudioAtrium\\Entity\\Discuss\\Post\\DAO\\PDOMySQL","dao_event":"dao_object_insert","entity_classname":"StudioAtrium\\Entity\\Discuss\\Post","entity_data":{"id":11196,"__foreign_props":[],"parent_id":"11134","cat_id":"100","project_id":"1144","nick":"James Ward","content":"Hello,\r\n\r\nMy name is James Ward, Senior Investment Consultant at Goldenshire, a private investment firm with offices in the U.S. and U.K. I\u2019m reaching out to explore potential partnerships with business and project owners seeking equity-based funding, strategic collaboration, or other financial solutions.\r\n\r\nGoldenshire focuses on mid- to long-term investments, supporting companies from start-up through growth, expansion, and later-stage development. We also provide financial services, including SBLC purchase\/lease and monetization, SBLC loans, and business funding solutions, with a strong emphasis on transparency and compliance.\r\n\r\nWe invest across multiple sectors, including real estate, construction, oil & gas, engineering, IT, agriculture, tourism, renewable energy, marine industries, industrial ventures, startups, and entertainment. Our approach typically involves acquiring a minority stake and working closely with management to provide both capital and strategic guidance for sustainable growth.\r\n\r\nIf you are seeking a committed funding partner, I would be glad to discuss how Goldenshire can align with your objectives. Please reply with your phone contact details so we can arrange a call at your convenience.\r\n\r\nYou can reach us directly at partnership@goldenshire.org\r\n\r\nKind regards,\r\n\r\nJames Ward\r\n\r\nSenior Investment Consultant\r\n\r\nGoldenshire Inc.\r\n\r\nGlobal Offices: U.S. & U.K.","create_date":"2025-09-09 10:52:23","modify_date":"2025-09-09 10:52:23","status":"published","is_moderated":0,"attachments":[],"_uid":2866223},"entity_changes":false}
